We are a mobile gaming development company that has produced a new app for the iPhone/iPad called Photo Contest! This app will be available on iTunes in just a few weeks.
We are looking for cross-promotional opportunities with another app developer that does photo editing.
Ideally, we would like to integrate a photo editing app into our photo game app to provide users with in-game editing. This joint venture would provide exposure for both of our apps and more download opportunities for each of our products.
We would like to discuss a revenue sharing plan that would be beneficial to both parties.
If you are interested in expanding your exposure and creating new revenue flow with this concept, please contact me.
Sincerely,
Keston Imhoff Vice President CloverLeaf Solutions, Inc.
